line_1: A moving prospect with fat herds replete,
line_2: Behold that grove, whose waving boughs admit,
With all that makes life's blessings sweet; —

line_1: The next begins: – Three canisters replete
line_2: With royal viands, and luxurious meat,

line_1: And view'd his form with ev'ry charm replete;
line_2: When still she found his languid pulses beat!

line_1: Her Mind, with each Virtue replete,
line_2: Who sought her to make them both blest:
